Paper: hep-th/0212180

Date: 2002-12-16

Title: The Kalb-Ramond field as a connection on a flat space time

Authors: M. Botta Cantcheff (CBPF, GFT)

Comments: 5 pages, no figures

We obtain a (Abelian) two form field as a connection on a flat space-time andits corresponding field strength is canonically constructed.